# Misc Commands

These commands are used to monitor and change the state of the model. These include: eleNodes

  • eleResponse Command
  • getTime Command
  • getEleTags Command
  • getNodeTags
  • loadConst
  • nodeCoord
  • nodeDisp
  • nodeVel
  • nodeAccel
  • nodeEigenvector
  • nodeBounds
  • print
  • printA
  • remove
  • reset
  • setTime
  • setMaxOpenFiles
  • testIter
  • testNorms
  • wipe
  • wipeAnalysis
  • exit Command
